features: Sufficient to Use and Replace: package includes 48 rolls of self adhesive bandage wraps, which are sufficient for you to use or replace in daily use, or satisfy other needs

With Elasticity and Breathability: these self adherent sport bandages adopt quality non woven porous fabric, which are soft and comfortable to touch, featuring good elasticity and breathability, friendly to skin and bring a comfortable using experience, won't cause discomforts during daily wearing

Self Adhesive Design: the self adherent sports tapes are properly self adherent, which just in a proper degree that won't stick to your skin and hair, and you can use the bandage wrapping for both people and pets, without worrying about it sticking to your or your pet's hair

Widely applicable: these athletic tapes can be applied to cover most of our body parts, such as ankle, wrist, finger, toe, elbow, knee and more, they can also work for pet, you can use the adhesive wrap to wrap wounds, fingers for golfing, first aid and joint support use, etc

Size Details: these self adhesive wraps measure approx. 5 cm/ 2 inches wide and 4.5 meters/ 5 yards long, which can be trimmed into a proper length to better fit your actual needs on some required occasions
description: Features:  Wide application: Bandage wrap rolls can not only be wrapped around body parts, but also a good bandage for pets. When your pet needs comfortable and supportive dressing, you can tie this self adhesive wrap to your pet, it can prevent the wound from getting worse during exercise and is a good tool for protecting the wound.  Convenient to use: These self adhering bandage wraps are not easy to loosen and fall off, which can allow you to do frequent readjustments.  Specifications: Material: non woven porous fabric Color: as shown in the picture Size: 2 inches x 5 yards/ 5 cm x 4.5 meters  Package includes: 48 x Self adherent sports tape  Notes: Manual measurement, please allow slight errors on size. The color may exist a slight difference due to different screen displays. Winding risk, keep away from little kids.
